  user_input {
    user_response: "# \360\237\217\203 Running Coach AI - Dashboard\n\n**Dashboard running minimalista con Chat AI, Groq + modelli premium per piani allenamento settimanali.**\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\216\257 Struttura\n\n- **\360\237\222\254 Chat** (DEFAULT) - Comunica con l\'IA\n  - Domande rapide \342\206\222 **Groq** (veloce, gratis)\n  - Piano allenamento \342\206\222 **Modello Premium** (GPT-4, Claude)\n  \n- **\360\237\223\212 Dashboard** - Statistiche e metriche\n  - Tot allenamenti, km, ore, ritmo medio, HR\n  - Ultimi 5 allenamenti\n  \n- **\360\237\223\234 History** - Storico completo di tutti gli allenamenti\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\232\200 Setup\n\n### 1. Python Environment\n```bash\ncd /Users/tommy/Desktop/tommy/tcx/ai-running-coach\npython3 -m venv .venv\nsource .venv/bin/activate\npip install -r requirements.txt\n```\n\n### 2. Config .env\n```\nGROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_key\nPREMIUM_API_KEY=your_openai_or_anthropic_key\nPREMIUM_MODEL=gpt-4-turbo  (o claude-3-opus-20240229)\nPREMIUM_API_BASE=https://api.openai.com/v1  (o anthropic per Claude)\n```\n\n### 3. Avvia Server\n```bash\npython app.py\n```\n\nVisita: `http://localhost:8502`\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\223\202 File Structure\n\n```\nai-running-coach/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 app.py                  # Flask server (minimalista)\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 core/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 parser.py          # TCX parsing (ottone)\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 llm_service.py     # Groq + modelli premium\n\342\224\202   \342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 memory.py          # JSON-based memory\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 data/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 activities.json    # Storico allenamenti\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 chat_history.json  # Chat history\n\342\224\202   \342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 training_plans.json # Piani salvati\n\342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 web/\n    \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 index.html         # SPA\n    \342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 assets/\n        \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 app.js         # Logica JS\n        \342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 styles.css     # CSS\n```\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\244\226 LLM Logic\n\n### Groq (Chat Veloce)\n- Per domande generali sull\'allenamento\n- Analisi metriche\n- Consigli form-based\n\n### Modello Premium (Piano Settimanale)\nRichieste contenenti keywords: \"piano\", \"settimana\", \"programma\", \"allenamento settimanale\"\n\nTrigger automatico al modello premium con cronologia chat\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\223\245 API Endpoints\n\n### Upload TCX\n```\nPOST /api/upload-tcx\nBody: FormData {file: .tcx}\nResponse: {success, activity}\n```\n\n### Chat\n```\nPOST /api/chat\nBody: {message: \"...\"}\nResponse: {user_message, assistant_response, is_plan}\n```\n\n### Stats\n```\nGET /api/stats\nResponse: {total_activities, total_km, total_duration_hours, avg_pace, avg_hr}\n```\n\n### Activities\n```\nGET /api/activities?limit=50\nResponse: {activities: [{...}]}\n```\n\n### Chat History\n```\nGET /api/chat-history\nPOST /api/chat-clear\n```\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\224\247 Customization\n\nModifica il system prompt in `app.py`:\n```python\nCOACH_SYSTEM_PROMPT = \"Sei un allenatore di corsa...\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\223\212 Parser TCX\n\nIl parser estrae:\n- Sport, ID attivit\303\240\n- Distanza (km), durata (min)\n- HR (media, max)\n- Cadenza (media, max)\n- Calorie consumate\n- Velocit\303\240 (media, max)\n- Dati per lap\n- Dispositivo (marca, modello)\n\nGestisce automaticamente TCX Garmin con estensioni custom.\n\n---\n\nCreato con \342\235\244\357\270\217 per runner seri.\n"
    items {
      text: "# \360\237\217\203 Running Coach AI - Dashboard\n\n**Dashboard running minimalista con Chat AI, Groq + modelli premium per piani allenamento settimanali.**\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\216\257 Struttura\n\n- **\360\237\222\254 Chat** (DEFAULT) - Comunica con l\'IA\n  - Domande rapide \342\206\222 **Groq** (veloce, gratis)\n  - Piano allenamento \342\206\222 **Modello Premium** (GPT-4, Claude)\n  \n- **\360\237\223\212 Dashboard** - Statistiche e metriche\n  - Tot allenamenti, km, ore, ritmo medio, HR\n  - Ultimi 5 allenamenti\n  \n- **\360\237\223\234 History** - Storico completo di tutti gli allenamenti\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\232\200 Setup\n\n### 1. Python Environment\n```bash\ncd /Users/tommy/Desktop/tommy/tcx/ai-running-coach\npython3 -m venv .venv\nsource .venv/bin/activate\npip install -r requirements.txt\n```\n\n### 2. Config .env\n```\nGROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_key\nPREMIUM_API_KEY=your_openai_or_anthropic_key\nPREMIUM_MODEL=gpt-4-turbo  (o claude-3-opus-20240229)\nPREMIUM_API_BASE=https://api.openai.com/v1  (o anthropic per Claude)\n```\n\n### 3. Avvia Server\n```bash\npython app.py\n```\n\nVisita: `http://localhost:8502`\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\223\202 File Structure\n\n```\nai-running-coach/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 app.py                  # Flask server (minimalista)\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 core/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 parser.py          # TCX parsing (ottone)\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 llm_service.py     # Groq + modelli premium\n\342\224\202   \342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 memory.py          # JSON-based memory\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 data/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 activities.json    # Storico allenamenti\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 chat_history.json  # Chat history\n\342\224\202   \342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 training_plans.json # Piani salvati\n\342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 web/\n    \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 index.html         # SPA\n    \342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 assets/\n        \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 app.js         # Logica JS\n        \342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 styles.css     # CSS\n```\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\244\226 LLM Logic\n\n### Groq (Chat Veloce)\n- Per domande generali sull\'allenamento\n- Analisi metriche\n- Consigli form-based\n\n### Modello Premium (Piano Settimanale)\nRichieste contenenti keywords: \"piano\", \"settimana\", \"programma\", \"allenamento settimanale\"\n\nTrigger automatico al modello premium con cronologia chat\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\223\245 API Endpoints\n\n### Upload TCX\n```\nPOST /api/upload-tcx\nBody: FormData {file: .tcx}\nResponse: {success, activity}\n```\n\n### Chat\n```\nPOST /api/chat\nBody: {message: \"...\"}\nResponse: {user_message, assistant_response, is_plan}\n```\n\n### Stats\n```\nGET /api/stats\nResponse: {total_activities, total_km, total_duration_hours, avg_pace, avg_hr}\n```\n\n### Activities\n```\nGET /api/activities?limit=50\nResponse: {activities: [{...}]}\n```\n\n### Chat History\n```\nGET /api/chat-history\nPOST /api/chat-clear\n```\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\224\247 Customization\n\nModifica il system prompt in `app.py`:\n```python\nCOACH_SYSTEM_PROMPT = \"Sei un allenatore di corsa...\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## \360\237\223\212 Parser TCX\n\nIl parser estrae:\n- Sport, ID attivit\303\240\n- Distanza (km), durata (min)\n- HR (media, max)\n- Cadenza (media, max)\n- Calorie consumate\n- Velocit\303\240 (media, max)\n- Dati per lap\n- Dispositivo (marca, modello)\n\nGestisce automaticamente TCX Garmin con estensioni custom.\n\n---\n\nCreato con \342\235\244\357\270\217 per runner seri.\n"
